     <p>You have the right to ask for unwanted information that you publicly post on the Internet to be removed if you are under the age of eighteen, live in California, and have an account with the website. Please use the contact details listed below to get in touch with us to request the removal of such data. Don't forget to include your account's email address and proof that you live in California. While we will take steps to ensure that the information is not made available to the public on the website, please be advised that the information might not be entirely erased from all of our systems (backups, for example).</p>
